  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> to a bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[11/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>– this is your <strong>chilli oil</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onions </strong>in half, then into thin strips</p><p>Slice your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways and scoop out the seeds with a spoon then slice into matchsticks, discard the seeds</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1704803038641-x200.jpg",
