            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Re-boil a kettle</p><p>While the fable mushrooms are in the oven, wash, then cut your <strong>pak choi</strong> in half, separating the <strong>white base[s]</strong> and <strong>green tops</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>hoisin sauce </strong>to a small bowl with a tiny splash of<strong> cold water </strong>to loosen it</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1704803044341-x200.jpg",
